Atsede Bayisa Tesema, onye a ma kwaara dị ka Atsede Bayisa (amụrụ na ụbọsị iri na isii n'ọnwa Eprel n'afọ 1987), bụ onye Etiopia na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge nke na-ahụ maka ihe omume ịgba ọsọ n'okporo ụzọ
O meriri Chicago Marathon, Boston Marathon na Paris Marathon ugboro abụọ

O nwetakwala mmeri na Xiamen International Marathon na Istanbul Marathon 
Ọ nọchitere anya Ethiopia na 2007 IAAF World Road Running Championships (na-ewere ọlaọcha otu) na 2009 World Championships in Athletics na ọsọ marathon
Ọ bụ onye nwetara ọlaọcha ọkara marathon n’afọ 2007 All-Africa Games.
Ọ malitere ọrụ mba ụwa ya site na arụmọrụ na Tokyo Women's Marathon na Nagano Marathon na 2006
Ọ gbara ọsọ na 2007 Rotterdam Marathon ma nwee oge nke 2:33:54 maka ọnọdụ nke anọ. Ihe omume mbụ ya bụ 2007 All-Africa Games, ebe o nwetara ọlaọcha nke ọkara marathon n'azụ Souad Aït Salem

Mgbe ọnwa ole na ole gachara, ọ gara 2007 IAAF World Road Running Championships wee mechie na nke iri na otu, na-enyere ụmụ nwanyị Etiopia aka inweta ọlaọcha. Mgbe nke a gasịrị, ọ gara n'ihu merie na Istanbul Marathon, na-edekọ ihe kachasị mma nke 2:29:05
O meghị ọganihu dị ịrịba ama na 2008, ebe ọ bụ na ọ bụ nke ise na Rome City Marathon na Toronto Marathon bụ ihe ndị dị mkpa n'afọ ya.

Na afọ 2009, ọ malitere site na njedebe nke itoolu na Dubai Marathon na oge nke 2:29:13. Mmeri n'oge kachasị mma nke 2:24:42 na Paris Marathon gosipụtara ọkwa ọhụrụ maka Baysa, ebe ọ meriri IAAF Gold Label Road Race mbụ ya. A họpụtara Baysa maka marathon ụmụ nwanyị na 2009 World Championships in Athletics, mana ọ dakwasịghị ụdị mbụ ya wee mechie na 27th ebe
Ọ gara n'ihu na-ewere ọnọdụ nke asaa na 2:32:05 na Frankfurt Marathon n'ọnwa Ọktoba.
Baysa malitere nke ọma n’afọ 2010 site n'ịghọ onye egwuregwu mba ọzọ mbụ meriri asọmpi ụmụ nwanyị na Xiamen International Marathon

Ọ butere ọsọ ahụ n'enweghị onye na-asọmpi ma mechie na 2:28:53. N'agbanyeghị ọnọdụ oyi, ọ merikwara Paris Half Marathon na Machị, na-edekọ oge nke 1:11:05. O setịpụrụ anya ya n'ịgbachitere aha ya na Paris Marathon n'ọnwa Eprel na usoro ịgba ọsọ ya n'ihu nwere ihe ịga nke ọma n'oge ndekọ: na-agwụcha n'ọnọdụ mbụ na 2:22:04, ọ meriri ihe ndekọ Marleen Renders nke guzo kemgbe afọ 2002 wee kụtuo ihe karịrị nkeji abụọ site na nke kachasị mma ya gara aga. Ọ gbara ọsọ na 2010 Chicago Marathon n'ọnwa Ọktoba wee malite nke ọma site na ịtọ ọsọ ọsọ site na mbido, na-eguzobe ọganihu dị ịrịba ama site na ọkara, ọ bụ ezie na ọ na-efu ya na njedebe, ọ meriri na oge nke 2:23:40, na-eti onye ịma aka ya kacha nso, Desiree Davila, site na nkeji abụọ, sekọnd iri anọ
Ọ banyere na Delhi Half Marathon na Nọvemba mana ọ bụ naanị nke ise n'ime ọkara.

Ọ meghere 2011 na Dubai Marathon, mana ọ gwụchara n'ọnọdụ nke ise ihe dị ka nkeji atọ n'azụ onye mmeri Aselefech Mergia. Ọnọdụ nke ise ọzọ bịara na 2011 London Marathon, ebe ọ nọ otu ebe n'azụ onye obodo ya Bezunesh Bekele. Ọ gbara ọsọ na agbụrụ abụọ nke France n'ọnwa Ọktoba: ọ bụ onye mmeri nke ọkara marathon na Reims à Toutes Jambes wee bụrụ onye nke abụọ na Lydia Cheromei na Marseille-Cassis Internationale.

Ọ gbara oge nke 2:23:13 awa na 2012 Dubai Marathon, nke bara uru naanị n'ọnọdụ nke asatọ na ọsọ ụmụ nwanyị. O meriri Tarsus Half Marathon na nkeji 69:39 na Machị tupu ọ gaa n'ihu na nke itoolu na 2012 London Marathon

Mgbe ọ na-agba ọsọ na 2012 Chicago Marathon, ọ dọtara ahụmahụ ya nke 2010 ma ghara ịda mbà na ọkara nke abụọ nke ọsọ ahụ, na-agbapụ na ngalaba ikpeazụ iji merie Rita Jeptoo maka ihe n'oge ahụ bụ aha ụmụ nwanyị Chicago mbụ ya (e nyere aha 2010 na 6 August 2015, na-esote nyocha IAAF). Ọ mechiri afọ ahụ site na ịrụ ọrụ dị elu na Montferland Run, na-emeri n'enweghị ihe ịma aka mgbe ọ hapụrụ ìgwè ahụ na kilomita 5 mbụ nke ọsọ ahụ.
O meriri na 2016 Boston Marathon, mana o nyere Bobbi Gibb iko ya; Gibb kwuru na 2017 ọ ga-aga n'obodo Baysaz nke Ethiopia ma weghachite ya.
